summary: AN ORDINANCE authorizing acquisition by real estate contract of Lots 5 and 8, Block 30, Addition to the Town of Seattle as laid out on the claims of C. D. Boren and A. A. Denny and M. L. Yesler (commonly known as C. D. Boren's Addition to the City of Seattle), making an appropriation from the Emergency Fund and declaring the emergency therefor.
